title: Director Interview
Application Type: I applied through an employee referral. The process took 8 weeks. I interviewed at Kauffman Foundation
Interview Descriptions: The interview process was thorough and all held in one day, which was convenient as I was from out of town.  Everyone was friendly, relaxed, and professional.  The questions were relevant.  A pretty good experience.
Interview Questions: How does your experience translate into advancing the mission of the organization?
